00:29:12,960 --> 00:29:15,378
- (bench closes)
- This is you.

304
00:29:15,379 --> 00:29:16,754
Ha, ha!

305
00:29:17,755 --> 00:29:19,299
Oh, wow.

306
00:29:20,133 --> 00:29:23,595
Oh, my God.
