00:31:32,474 --> 00:31:36,810
♪ To try and make you mine ♪

330
00:31:36,811 --> 00:31:41,316
♪ And I think
I'm gonna love you ♪

331
00:31:42,525 --> 00:31:47,905
♪ For a long, long time ♪

